name: Vessels 083: The Blue Duchess
description: The cocktail of drugs and nutrients that need to be pumped into a human body to keep it alive during suspended animation can have the side-effect of turning the recipient’s lips a deathly shade of blue. Since the last remnants of humanity arrived on this cursed world, humanity has had no more need for suspended animation, but the drugs have the convenient side-effect of prolonging human life, and for that the wealthy will pay a high price…
